## Boostrap code


# We want to work in $home
cd 

# First update the Apt repo
sudo apt-get update

# Then get Git
sudo apt-get install git

# We can then clone the project
mkdir project
cd project
git clone https://github.com/maxsu/Coffeebot
cd Coffeebot


# Run the puppet install code
sudo ./deploy-puppet

# And then the wordpress install code
sudo ./deploy-wordpress


